gin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://img01.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i1/22502473/T2SzLqXbVaXXXXXXXX_!!22502473.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\"><img alt=\"\" align=\"absMiddle\" style=\"border-right: 0px; border-top: 0px; vertical-align: top; border-left: 0px; border-bottom: 0px\" src=\"http://img04.taobaocdn.com/imgextra/i4/22502473/T23qt6XeFdXXXXXXXX_!!22502473.jpg\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">目前安卓2.3以上的平板电脑基本都是可以使用的，但也不包括有部分不能兼容，买家请慎重考虑后在下单，不能使用本公司概不负责。</p>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 1.12em 0px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">平板电脑用户选择网卡方法: &nbsp;朋友们在选择网卡时.只要能确认好平板电脑上的接口是怎样的然后选择一款与之相应接口的网卡就可以了.别的不用考虑了.因为接口对了,网卡的协议都是一样的.可以通用.</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">平板电脑用户使用有线网卡步骤: &nbsp;首先要确认好自已的网线是不是经过路由器.如网线不经过路由器的朋友,一定要注意自已平板没有没拔号上网功能,如有可以用网卡.反之不能用. &nbsp;网线经过路由器的朋友设置方法很简单.先把网线联接好.之后把平板无线网功能关闭.把以太网功能打勾,等平板电脑上有联接提示出现就可以上网了.</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">使用不了的情况:根据本人经验.如平板接无线网卡无法使用可能有以下几种: 1 平板电脑无以太网功能. 2有以太网功能但无效无法打勾选取.3 网卡与平板电脑之间接触不良.</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">笔计本台试机用户选择网卡方法: &nbsp;使用笔计本与台试机的朋友选择网卡只有一种接口那就是USB接口.但在选择时要注意一点的就是如亲的电脑系统是XP的那就可以选取本店内所有USB的网卡.如电脑系系统是WIN7 64位的或WIN 8的朋友就要选择支持WIN7 64位的网卡.这时千万不能搞错.摘错了是用不了的.</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">重点说明：现在工厂生产网卡时都不带驱动盘了.这是种环保理念.很多朋友收到货时不知如何安装驱动.在这里作一下说明: &nbsp;当朋友们拿到网卡时,把网线联接好后.可以从网上下载一个&quot;驱动精灵&quot; 这个从百度直接可以搜到的,然后把软件下载下装到电脑上.打开驱动精灵软件,在驱动管理里直接把有线网驱动更新就可以了.( &nbsp;这是对笔计本与台试电脑用户的说明.使用平板电脑的朋友无需关心,平板电脑无需安装驱动)</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">特别提醒：平板电脑不支持拨号上网，必须是连接从路由器连出来的网线。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">满足以下条件的【平板电脑】则可直接拍下，即插即用哦。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">平板系统是安卓系统（此条件基本都满足）</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">支持以太网的平板电脑 （以太网：通俗的解释为从路由器引出来的网线 而不是从猫引出来的网线。如顾客不清楚自己的平板是否支持以太网，则可以联系客服 说明下平板的型号，我们帮您解决）</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">平板本身自带U口（USB母口）或者平板自带OTG线的 都可以。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">满足以上条件的顾客，可以直接拍下 即插即用。我们会在您拍下的第一时间安排发货。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">下面我们以盈方平板为例：</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">1.在平板桌面找到设置那一项打开。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">2.找到无线和网络，把Wi-Fi关闭，把移动网络关闭</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">3.找到以太网设置，点开进入，把以太网钩选打开</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">4.点以太网配置，在连接类型 选择DHCP动太获取后，就会自动搜索IP地址了。点保存，下次上网就不用设置了。</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">5.返回桌面，点浏览器就可以上网了</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">笔记本 台式机</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">Windows 98SE/2000/ME/XP/VISTA,MAC OS8.6 （如果安装对应驱动，联系客服发给你）</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">完全包含网卡功能，硬件支持TCP/IP、NETBEUI、IPX/SPX网络协议</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(255,255,255); widows: 2; orphans: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">共享网络资源，如Adsl、Modem、CD-ROM、打印机、扫描仪等</div>\r\n<div style=\"word-spacing: 0px; font: 14px/21px tahoma, arial, 宋体, sans-serif; text-transform: none; color: rgb(64,64,64); text-indent: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(2