; font: 12px/22px \'arial verdana sans-serif lucida grande lucida sans unicode 宋体\'; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">TL-WN725N采用全新微型外观设计，精致微小，使用时不会占用空间，同时便于携带。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 19px 0px 6px; word-spacing: 0px; font: bold 14px/22px \'arial verdana sans-serif lucida grande lucida sans unicode 宋体\'; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,102,255); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">良好的兼容性</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/22px \'arial verdana sans-serif lucida grande lucida sans unicode 宋体\'; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,0,0); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">TL-WN725N良好兼容市面上的11b、11g、11n产品，同时支持主流的高清播放机、IPTV机顶盒及互联网电视。</p>\r\n<h3 style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 19px 0px 6px; word-spacing: 0px; font: bold 14px/22px \'arial verdana sans-serif lucida grande lucida sans unicode 宋体\'; text-transform: none; color: rgb(0,102,255); text-indent: 0px; padding-top: 0px; white-space: normal; letter-spacing: normal; background-color: rgb(240,240,242); orphans: 2; widows: 2; -webkit-text-size-adjust: auto; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px\">良好的无线性能</h3>\r\n<p style=\"padding-right: 0px; padding-left: 0px; padding-bottom: 0px; margin: 0px 0px 10px; word-spacing: 0px; font: 12px/22px \'arial verdana sans-serif lucida grande lucida san